[0.604, "o", "  \u001b[31m\u001b[1mThe danger:\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[31m  ‚ÄĘ leaked .env = full wallet access, unlimited USDC\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[31m  ‚ÄĘ prompt injection ‚Üí agent bets everything\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[31m  ‚ÄĘ no daily cap ‚ÄĒ a bad session = all funds gone\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[31m  ‚ÄĘ no kill switch ‚ÄĒ can't stop a rogue agent\u001b[0m\r\n"]
